data.description: Opportunity knocks! Here's your chance to build some sweat equity with this affordable home! In a great neighborhood and situated on a double lot, this raised ranch is awaiting your finishing touches. While there is work to be done, many of the expensive items have already been taken care of in the last 5 years.  The main level features 2 bedrooms, bathroom, eat-in kitchen and living room. The lower level is a blank canvas- an English basement that is ready to be finished to your liking. Don't miss this opportunity! Home being sold as-is.
